# Lab Setup

## Objective

Build an enterprise Active Directory homelab using Windows Server 2022 and VMware.

## Environment

Virtualization Platform:
- VMware Workstation

Server:
- DC01
- Windows Server 2022 Standard

Domain:
- gallegos.local

Network Configuration:

IP Address:
192.168.10.10

Subnet Mask:
255.255.255.0

Gateway:
192.168.10.1

DNS:
192.168.10.10

## Installed Roles

- Active Directory Domain Services
- DNS Server
- DHCP Server

## Organizational Units

- IT
- HR
- Sales
- Workstations
- Servers

## Purpose

This environment simulates a small enterprise infrastructure used for identity management, access control, and shared resources.
